snippet.textDisplay:
It seems like a lot of people's spirits are broken. Don't give up. 

Start thinking differently. Change your perceptual State of mind. When you change the way you think that change is your behavior.

Don't give up. We have the power as we are 8 billion strong. Everything ends when we awaken and come together.

There needs to be a personal revolution, it has to happen inside first.
